---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const pageTitle = "Our Philosophy — Student-Centered, Exam-Ready";
const pageDescription = "Grifi's philosophy for students, teachers, and institutes: learning, mastery, discipline, health, and exam temperament.";
---

<Layout {title}={pageTitle} {description}={pageDescription}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 via-teal-50 to-cyan-50 py-24">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-5"></div>
    <div class="container relative mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary">
          <span class="text-lg">🎯</span>
          Our Philosophy
        </div>
        <h1 class="mb-6 text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          Student-centered learning for
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-600 via-emerald-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            competitive excellence
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Grifi is reimagining how we learn by placing the student at the center of every learning environment. 
          Teachers act as mentors and gurus who guide, challenge, and support. Institutes provide structure, 
          accountability, and community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ecosystem Section -->
  <section id="ecosystem" class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">The Learning Ecosystem</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Three pillars work together to create transformative learning experiences
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-400 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl border bg-card p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/15 text-2xl">
            🎓
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Student at the Center</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Every decision optimizes for the learner's clarity, momentum, and confidence. Progress
            should feel visible, personalized, and motivating.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-cyan-400 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl border bg-card p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-teal-500/15 text-2xl">
            🧘‍♂️
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Teacher as Mentor & Guru</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            The teacher guides the journey—setting direction, calibrating difficulty, and cultivating
            discipline and curiosity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-emerald-400 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl border bg-card p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-cyan-500/15 text-2xl">
            🏛️
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Institute as Scaffolding</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Institutes create the rhythm: timetables, milestones, feedback loops, and peer energy—so
            serious preparation becomes sustainable.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Journey Section -->
  <section id="journey" class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">The Learning Journey</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Preparation is a journey with distinct, reinforcing parts. Our tools strengthen each part while keeping the whole in view.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border bg-card p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-bl from-emerald-500/10 to-transparent rounded-full -translate-y-16 translate-x-16"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/15 text-lg">
            📚
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Learn actively, not passively. Convert concepts into your own words, solve short problems as you
            read, teach back to a peer or to yourself. Understanding compounds when you engage.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border bg-card p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-bl from-teal-500/10 to-transparent rounded-full -translate-y-16 translate-x-16"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-500/15 text-lg">
            🎯
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Mastery</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Mastery blends two axes: how much you retain and how difficult the material you can handle is.
            We support techniques that raise both.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></div>
              <span class="text-sm"><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Active recall</span> and <span class="font-semibold text-foreground">elaboration</span> to make knowledge retrievable.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500"></div>
              <span class="text-sm"><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Spaced repetition</span> to fight forgetting and stabilize memory.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-500"></div>
              <span class="text-sm"><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Interleaving</span> to build flexible understanding across topics.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></div>
              <span class="text-sm">The <span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Goldilocks zone</span>: practice that is not too easy, not too hard—just beyond comfort.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500"></div>
              <span class="text-sm"><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Progressive overload</span>: gradated question sets that expand depth and breadth over time.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border bg-card p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-bl from-cyan-500/10 to-transparent rounded-full -translate-y-16 translate-x-16"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/15 text-lg">
            ⏰
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Discipline</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Consistency beats intensity. Schedules, streaks, and tiny wins keep momentum. We design
            friction-light workflows so showing up is the default.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border bg-card p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-bl from-emerald-500/10 to-transparent rounded-full -translate-y-16 translate-x-16"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/15 text-lg">
            🌱
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Health</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Learning should fit real life. Some of our tools are designed so students can learn while
            walking in the park—audio prompts, quick recall, and light-touch reviews.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border bg-card p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 md:col-span-2">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-48 h-48 bg-gradient-to-bl from-teal-500/10 to-transparent rounded-full -translate-y-24 translate-x-24"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-500/15 text-lg">
            🧠
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Exam Temperament</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Tests reward calm, clarity, and pacing. We simulate real conditions, provide time-bound drills,
            and help you develop a steady, confident rhythm for exam day.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Competitive Exams Section -->
  <section id="competitive-exams" class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 via-teal-50 to-cyan-50 p-12 shadow-xl">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-5"></div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary/15 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary">
            <span class="text-lg">🏆</span>
            Competitive Excellence
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Built for competitive exams</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Competitive preparation demands both speed and depth. Our AI tools craft question sets in the
            Goldilocks zone, schedule spaced reviews automatically, and surface weak spots before they cost
            marks.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 mb-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/15 text-xl">
              ⚡
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Speed & Depth</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Optimized for competitive exam requirements</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-teal-500/15 text-xl">
              🎯
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Goldilocks Zone</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Perfect difficulty level for growth</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-cyan-500/15 text-xl">
              📊
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Progress Tracking</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Aligned views for all stakeholders</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-primary-foreground font-medium shadow-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all">
            <span>🚀</span>
            Explore tools
          </a>
          <a href="/students" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border bg-white/50 px-6 py-3 font-medium hover:bg-white/80 transition-all">
            <span>🎓</span>
            For students
          </a>
          <a href="/teachers" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border bg-white/50 px-6 py-3 font-medium hover:bg-white/80 transition-all">
            <span>👨‍🏫</span>
            For teachers
          </a>
          <a href="/institutes" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border bg-white/50 px-6 py-3 font-medium hover:bg-white/80 transition-all">
            <span>🏛️</span>
            For institutes
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Promise Section -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border bg-card p-12 text-center shadow-xl">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-bl from-primary/5 to-transparent rounded-full -translate-y-32 translate-x-32"></div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary">
          <span class="text-lg">✨</span>
          Our Promise
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">A simple promise</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8">
          If a student is truly at the center, everything else should get simpler: what to study now,
          how to practice next, and how to know you are improving. That is what we build.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full bg-primary px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium text-primary-foreground shadow-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all">
          <span>🚀</span>
          Try our AI tools →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .bg-grid-pattern {
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 20px 20px;
  }
</style> 